      <abstract encodinganalog="description">The David Baddley independent film collection (1980s) consists of two experimental films Baddley made while studying at the University of Utah.  David Baddley is a Salt Lake City based artist; he teaches at Westminster College.  This collection is part of the Utah Independent Film Archive (UIFA).</abstract>
