          <p>1. "Grass Bolex Plus-X Guitar," an experimental film composed of motion-blurred shots of grass with an electric guitar soundtrack.  Originally shot on 16mm film.</p>
          <p>2. "Relay," an experimental short about a person running.  The film was shot from the point of view of the runner and was edited in-camera.  Originally shot on Super 8mm film.</p>
